parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the passenger airbag sensor can cause the airbag to not deploy in the event of a crash, putting the passenger at risk of serious injury or death.
symptoms: The passenger airbag off light is illuminated
the airbag warning light is flashing
the passenger airbag does not recognize an adult person sitting in the seat
the airbag is deactivated even with an adult passenger in the seat.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag system can cause the airbags to not deploy in the event of a crash, putting the occupants at risk of serious injury or death.

the airbag sensor is faulty
the airbag system is bypassed.
